<page_title>Centrifugal reaction force</page_title>
<text>
Centrifugal reaction force

  
      
Stopping the ball when it reaches the upper half of the circular track will cause it to fall off, 
because of the lack of the centrifugal reaction force, which is proportional to the square of speed.</text>
