<paragraph start="29" end="32">
<Alignment>1</Alignment>
<content start="29" end="30">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageTextBox</class>
<width>360.0</width>
<height>250.0</height>
<title>&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;
    If the ball at the bottom starts with a speed that is high enough, it can 
    pass the highest point of the circular track without falling down, as if 
    some kind of force were holding it onto the track. This effect is called 
    the centrifugal reaction force.

    &lt;p&gt;
      In fact, you may experience the centrifugal reaction force every day --- 
      it is the force that you feel when the vehicle you are riding makes a 
      turn.
    &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</title>
<opaque>false</opaque>
</component></content>

<content start="30" end="31">
<component><class>org.concord.mw2d.activity.AtomContainer</class>
<resource>centrifugal$0.mml</resource><menubar>false</menubar><statusbar>false</statusbar><border>none</border></component></content>

<content start="31" end="32">
</content>

</paragraph>
<paragraph start="32" end="39">
<Alignment>1</Alignment>
<content start="32" end="33">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageSlider</class>
<modelclass>org.concord.mw2d.models.MolecularModel</modelclass>
<model>0</model>
<value>5.0</value>
<minimum>0.0</minimum>
<maximum>10.0</maximum>
<nstep>20</nstep>
<title>Set the initial speed when the ball is at the bottom</title>
<width>320</width>
<height>80</height>
<opaque>false</opaque>
<disabled_at_run>true</disabled_at_run>
<tick>true</tick>
<script>set atom[%ball].vx 500+%val*200;
set atom[%ball].vy 0;
set atom[%ball].rx 20;
set atom[%ball].ry 21.5;</script>
<change>Execute MW script</change>
</component></content>

<content start="33" end="34">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageButton</class>
<title>Run</title>
<modelclass>org.concord.mw2d.models.MolecularModel</modelclass>
<model>0</model>
<disabled_at_run>true</disabled_at_run>
<script>run</script>
<action>Execute MW script</action>
</component></content>

<content start="34" end="35">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageButton</class>
<title>Stop</title>
<modelclass>org.concord.mw2d.models.MolecularModel</modelclass>
<model>0</model>
<script>stop</script>
<action>Execute MW script</action>
</component></content>

<content start="35" end="36">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageButton</class>
<title>Reset</title>
<modelclass>org.concord.mw2d.models.MolecularModel</modelclass>
<model>0</model>
<script>reset</script>
<action>Execute MW script</action>
</component></content>

<content start="36" end="37">
</content>

<content start="37" end="38">
<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageButton</class>
<title>Stop the ball</title>
<modelclass>org.concord.mw2d.models.MolecularModel</modelclass>
<model>0</model>
<script>set atom[%ball].vx 0;
set atom[%ball].vy 0;</script>
<action>Execute MW script</action>
</component></content>

